lines: 1. Natogende intwe twensi,as' emeremo yayeNatokore nomogoko,ne chinguru chionsi,'banto bonsi baganyete,as' ogokonywa gwaito,Natobatang'ane bona,enchera y'Omonene.
Nchwo togend', as' omogondo,as' emeremo yaye,Nonya 'meke, gos' emenge,ninyekore nomokia,'Banto bonsi, nimbakonye,nobwanchani, nobuya,Nchwo 'Monene, nkonye bono,nkore emeremo yane.
2. Natogende, aborokia,as enyomba ya Nyasae,Toborokie abanto bonsi,chingencho chia Nyasae,Titokwa Moyo,as' ense tiga tosabe mono,Erio natong'use abange,ase Omokonyi Oito.
3. Natokonye Abakristo,as' emeremo yaye,Kabe ang'e koyeimokia,'mesigo 'merito,Tab'ang'e gochiimokia'gurube chindito,Natoike seito bori,as' Obonda bwa Yeso.
